
Do it in Local System then
we can do it in Remote System
- Read the file uploaded by the user
and store them in the Cloud Bucket


Create a Google Service Account :
https://docs.cloudera.com/HDPDocuments/HDP3/HDP-3.1.0/bk_cloud-data-access/content/gcs-create-service-account.html

Why Service Account :

We are creating a Private Bucket.
Our Code needs to get access to this Private Bucket
If the Bucket is PUBLIC, then it can easily upload any files or delete files


